---
// src/pages/index.astro
---
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <title>My K8s Portfolio</title>
    <style>
      body { font-family: sans-serif; max-width: 800px; margin: 40px auto; padding: 0 20px; line-height: 1.6; background: #fafafa; color: #333; }
      nav { margin-bottom: 40px; }
      nav a { margin-right: 20px; text-decoration: none; color: #007acc; font-weight: bold; }
      .hero { background: #007acc; color: white; padding: 30px; border-radius: 8px; margin-bottom: 30px; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <nav>
      <a href="/">Home</a>
      <a href="/portfolio">Portfolio</a>
    </nav>

    <div class="hero">
      <h1>Hello, I'm a Cloud & DevOps Engineer 👋</h1>
      <p>Specializing in cloud-native ecosystems, automation, and Kubernetes orchestration.</p>
    </div>

    <h2>About This Site</h2>
    <p>
      This portfolio isn't just hosted on a standard static platform—it's engineered. It is fully containerized using <strong>Docker</strong>, orchestrated via <strong>Kubernetes</strong>, and deployed through an automated <strong>GitOps</strong> pipeline.
    </p>

    <h2>Core Stack</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Orchestration:</strong> Kubernetes (K3s, Minikube)</li>
      <li><strong>CI/CD & GitOps:</strong> GitHub Actions, ArgoCD</li>
      <li><strong>IaC:</strong> Terraform</li>
    </ul>
  </body>
</html>